The Medical Technology Licensure Examinations took place on Saturday, August 31, and Sunday, September 1, 2013, in Cebu, Baguio, and Manila.

For those who would be registering later for their Professional Identification Card (ID), they are required to bring the following:

1 short brown envelope with name and profession

Accomplished Oath Form

2 sets of metered documentary stamps

Community Tax certificate (current)

1 piece passport size picture (colored with white background and complete nametag)
